def mixed_mt0y0w(x, y):
    t1 = jnp.sqrt(jnp.abs(x))
    t2 = jnp.power(jnp.abs(t1), jnp.abs(y) % 3 + 1)
    t3 = jnp.sum(t2)
    return t3
